This paper deals with the problem of designing optimal auctions, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and algorithmic mechanism design (cs.DS). The paper also involves the use of mathematical optimization techniques to obtain closed-form solutions, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.IT). Finally, the paper is focused on revenue optimization, which is a key aspect of computational economics (cs.EC).
